OL,11,CG2021FFrank Mitchell presents the
OL,12,Flocal weather forecast on UTV for the
OL,13,Ffinal time, after 37 years with the
OL,14,Fcompany. He ended the weather bulletin
OL,15,Fwith his familiar sign-off: "Take care.
OL,16,FBe good. Bye bye".
